# uptimerobot_current_user (Data Source)

Reads account metadata for the UptimeRobot user authenticated by the configured API key, including the current plan, monitor usage, monitor limit, and SMS credits.

This data source is read-only. Values can change outside Terraform when account usage or subscription state changes. The `email` attribute is marked sensitive to avoid displaying it in Terraform output, but Terraform state still stores the value.

